  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blueprints is a 3D third-person parkour platformer game where the more levels you beat, the more complex they get.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Experience beautiful grid-textured landscapes in this short casual adventure you are very likely to forget. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play all sorts of parkour challenges (and 2 minutes of holding the W key) in this adventure of a lifetime.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Not to be confused with the 2025 puzzle game Blue Prince <span class=\"bb_strike\">(but please do confuse them it gives me more money)</span></i></p>",
